    <detaileddescription>
<para>Requires `flush(<ref refid="classhelios_1_1engine_1_1runtime_1_1world_1_1GameWorld" kindref="compound">GameWorld</ref>&amp;, <ref refid="classhelios_1_1engine_1_1runtime_1_1world_1_1UpdateContext" kindref="compound">UpdateContext</ref>&amp;) noexcept` and `clear() noexcept` (via HasClear). Types satisfying this concept can be wrapped by the type-erased CommandBuffer wrapper.</para>
